attributionInfo.brokerName: RE/MAX at Barnegat Bay - Forked River

data.description: VIEWS!VIEWS!VIEWS!   Newly renovated with many upgrades.  This is a gorgeous home!  Spectacular Bay Views from the living room and front two story deck. Serene views from the rear enclosed porch perfect for an extra room with a sofa sleeper. Updated kitchen boasts all newer appliances plus a washer and dryer. 2 nice size bedrooms with water views.  Newer bathrooms and many more enhancements. Lots of closets.  Storage closet off the front deck and shed available for additional storage. Treat yourself to the year round living at its best or a vacation home to enjoy.  Right across from the public dock where you can relax in the gazebo, fish, crab or launch your boat. The heated pool is right in the complex. Great summer fun with concerts at Barnegat dock across the street, bay beach walking distance . Convenient location for local shopping and transportation. Treat yourself to the good life! More photos coming soon
